<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ry Jeso, Tompon'aina !
 Nalevina Hianao,
 Kanefa he, deraina,
 Fa velona ao izao !

[V2]
 Ny fasana nivoha
 Noho ny herinao,
 Fa tsy mba nahatoha
 Ny voninahitrao !

[V3]
 Ireo miaramila
 Nahery sy nahay
 Dia tsy mba nahatana
 Anao Mpanjakanay !

[V4]
 Nitsangana tokoa,
 Ho tena santatray,
 Hianao, ry Tompo soa
 Sy Kapiteninay !</lyrics>
<title>Ry Jeso Tompon'aina! FFPM136</title>
<author>H. Lahee</author>
<hymn_number>136</hymn_number>
</song>